nodes.text: 'Jabba's Palace Sealed Deck's were promotional products created by Decipher in October 2000, as an addition to the Star Wars Customizable Card Game (or SWCCG). They are a product that contains cards which in conjunction with Jabba's Palace and Enhanced Jabba's Palace, chronicle the first portion of Return of the Jedi for the SWCCG.
